corr_each = function(df){
  res = cor.test(~ perc_genes + Paco_Best_effectsize, data=df, method='spearman')
  data.frame(COG_category = first(df$COG_category),
             effect = res$statistic,
             rho = res$estimate,
             pval = res$p.value)
}

emap_fss = emap_fs %>%
  group_split.(COG_category) %>%
  lapply(corr_each) %>%
  rbindlist(use.names=TRUE) %>%
  mutate.(padj = p.adjust(as.Num(pval), method='fdr'))

cat_each = function(df){
  res = wilcox.test(Paco_Best_effectsize~score_cat, data=df)
  data.frame(phenotype = first(df$phenotype),
             effect = res$statistic,
             pval = res$p.value)
}

corr_each = function(df){
  res = cor.test(~ marker_count + Paco_Best_effectsize, data=df, method='spearman')
  data.frame(DATABASE = first(df$DATABASE),
             effect = res$statistic,
             rho = res$estimate,
             pval = res$p.value)
}

  filter.(!is.na(DATABASE),

  mutate.(X = paste('p =', round(padj,3), sep=' '))
